  "detailed_description": "This game is an online First person shooter game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the game there will be two teams for you to choose from, that is.<br />\r\n<br />\r\norange delivery<br />\r\nand<br />\r\ngreen delivery<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn each game map, there will be weapons for you to choose from. You can choose your class before choosing a room to play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe playing mode system is as follows.<br />\r\n- team deathmatch<br />\r\nKill an opposing player<br />\r\n- free for all<br />\r\nKill all players in the game.<br />\r\n- capture the flag<br />\r\nhoist the flag of the opposite side<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can increase or decrease the number of bots before starting the game.",
  "about_the_game": "This game is an online First person shooter game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the game there will be two teams for you to choose from, that is.<br />\r\n<br />\r\norange delivery<br />\r\nand<br />\r\ngreen delivery<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn each game map, there will be weapons for you to choose from. You can choose your class before choosing a room to play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe playing mode system is as follows.<br />\r\n- team deathmatch<br />\r\nKill an opposing player<br />\r\n- free for all<br />\r\nKill all players in the game.<br />\r\n- capture the flag<br />\r\nhoist the flag of the opposite side<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can increase or decrease the number of bots before starting the game.",
